{"tid":1716950,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"彈門唔通真係咁容易?","createTime":"2019-11-13T13:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:05:17.000Z","uid":320717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7cc3ca132e1a3c1d6ed5264eac07343c56c9ba2b","tid":1716950,"uid":320717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"今朝搭地鐵, 好奇怪冇人擋門, 都彈左好多次門<br />\n之後見到傍邊個西裝友, 原來每次門就來關上時就用對皮鞋啜住個門, 增加關門時的阻力<br />\n雖然最後對門都關上, 但每一次都彈番轉頭<br />\n彈左廿次, 可能條西裝友可能玩厭, 冇用對鞋啜住, 個門就冇彈了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條西裝友仲氣定神閒咁玩緊手機, 如果唔係咁啱我企係佢隔離, 再加上我細心睇, 我都唔知原來佢就係令個門彈左咁耐的暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇可能對門咁易就彈? 有冇人知咩原理? 大家千萬唔可以咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c13f3f1a1fecd9f6ca8300cbbf6b485273cb2f","tid":1716950,"uid":23739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6fede6fd1828398394e6179c23d169c11fcd81c","tid":1716950,"uid":247673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8979be5598d001587ad60313a6e6f0fb081ba6","tid":1716950,"uid":247673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}